title: Visitor_Garrison_Greeting
---
Soldier: Trader. I'm looking for a sidearm. Quick.
-> What have you got to trade?
    Soldier: Two boxes of 5.45. AP rounds. Want them?
    -> I'll take them.
        Soldier: Smart choice.
    -> Not interested.
        Soldier: Your loss.
-> I'm not selling today.
    Soldier: ...fine. I'll find someone else.
===
